title: of 2018), the reference to Dublin Institute of Technology in Schedule 3 to the
heading: It is hereby declared that the reference to Dublin Institute of Technology
text_raw:
2. 

It is hereby declared that the reference to Dublin Institute of Technology 
in Schedule 3 to the National Treasury Management Agency (Amendment) Act 
2014 (No. 23 of 2014) shall cease to have effect. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

31 August, 2022. 

MICHAEL MCGRATH, 

Minister for Public Expenditure and Reform. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 9th September, 2022.
